title: Natura Si - Romolo
description: Part of chain of organic food and products store throughout Milan and northern Italy. Has a deli. Organic, vegan, vegetarian, macrobiotic, gluten-free, sugar-free products, natural cleaning products and toiletries, pet food, and organic, supplements, beauty products, and books. Note: Metro, train, bus, and tram links all connect to Romolo in the south of the city.
